title: Breaking: Tucumcari vs. Eunice game cancelled
text:
Breaking: Tucumcari vs. Eunice game cancelled Kyle Henderson Talk about it in NEW MEXICO PREP FOOTBALL INSIDER 
NMPreps.com learned today that a current high school student at Tucumcari High School was tragically killed in a shooting accident. The Tucumcari vs. Eunice match up which was scheduled for October 2nd, 2014 has been cancelled according to Tucumcari officials. This is a developing story. More to follow.
